  <channel>
    <title>CKAN: Ticket #2839: Specifying sort order breaks search results on group page</title>
    <link>http://localhost/ticket/2839</link>
    <description>&lt;p&gt;
Create a group, create some datasets and add them to the group, then view the group's page with a sort-order specified in the URL, e.g. {{/group/foo?q=&amp;amp;sort=title_string+asc}}, no datasets are displayed even though there are datasets in the group that match the search query. Remove the sort order from the URL and the datasets will appear.
&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
